title: Chicken & Creamy Parmesan Sauce with Garlic Mash & Zesty Veggies
description: What's a quick and easy way to bring a rich, home-style flavour to a dish? Add our popular spice blend - Nan's special seasoning,
with paprika, pepper, onion and garlic! Use it to coat the chicken breast, then add a rich Parmesan sauce and mashed potato for a dish that's all kinds of yum.

